[x] AWS CloudWatch sink
[ ] Grafana Loki sink
[ ] Config file schema (TOML)
[ ] Windows build in CI

:NOTE
logdrop intentionally has no plugin system and no daemon mode. Every feature ships in the binary
or not at all. This keeps the attack surface small and the install story dead simple.
If you need orchestration, wrap it in systemd or a Dockerfile — it plays well with both.

